{"tid":1362011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想衝的入黎睇睇，分析post/[勇武入]長文分析圍村部署，點解唔好入村","createTime":"2019-07-24T17:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:43:13.000Z","uid":259987,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b4339c4505261e30ad82f87a3c4bc3c16930b5","tid":1362011,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:47:57.000Z","msg":"開得戰，不外乎天時地利人和 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">天時：</span></strong><br />\n1. 這次遊行召集時間 1630-2400(好似話想提早到1500), 但係大家都知香港人出名遲到，隨時入黑先行到，而黑社會話明黑，夜晚先係佢哋主場，加上記者要影到你都要有燈光。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 早一星期已經講到話要搞村，D村民一早有準備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地利：</span></strong><br />\n圍村村口前面係car park 非常空曠，進入時被村民一目了然。入圍村只有一條路，會裝有CCTV。一入圍村，戰友會係入侵方，有好多隱蔽既小路只有村民先知道，入面既村屋又係村民既地盤，村民可以在天台扔花盆，佢地有大量大型車輛，可以係入村後隨時封路，四面受敵，前線要提防所有村入面既人。<br />\n係南邊圍入面有四個一級歷史建築&mdash;晉源押、同益棧、大王廟同埋玄關二帝廟，絕對唔可以毀壞。除外村內會有民居、村校同埋教會。<br />\n十八鄉因歷史問題，來往非常密切，南邊圍、西邊圍、東頭圍、英龍圍、大圍村合稱五和同氣連枝，北面仲有林氏山貝村，所以一旦有事，戰友要向南面退，大馬路地方有限，東南角是Yoho既地盤。人潮唯有向水門頭天橋撤﹐而落橋位係泰祥街水車館街，人煙密集。<br />\n十八鄉和八鄉村民來往頗密，平時村裡的活動亦會邀請對方參與，逃走時避免去錦上路方向。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人和：</span></strong><br />\n<strong>自已友：</strong>按前幾次經驗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00VeHm0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00VeHm0.png&h=d3c5a211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>對家：</strong><br />\n據報，係7月21日，白衫有500-800人，當中包括睇水、車隊，相信打手有300人。而整個幫會好大機會有上千人，亦有未知多少刀手。<br />\n刀方面以開山刀為主。佢地重視威信建立，會因內部傷亡而報復。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而香港原居民有70萬人，是次既事件由南邊圍(及十八鄉部份其他鄉村)既鄉黑所為。<br />\n圍村人非常重視祠堂同圍村傳統，將祠堂視為社交重地及集體回憶，若然燒村/祠堂就會得罪本來不涉事既居民，包括中立甚至是黃營的村民。另外，佢地有不少祠堂，會有燒錯祠堂，樹立不必要敵人既可能。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n村民對外非常團結，村民之間社交網絡完整，會將村內發生既事以whatsapp通報全村。我地早一星期已經開始召集人手，放風燒村毀祠，咁樣就算搬出村外既村民都會返去元朗入面保護家園，巴打搵咗十八鄉既人口分佈，如下圖所示:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inpryuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinpryuM.png&h=7e498f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ni.e. 會出動的原居民(20-60 男丁) 有機會過5000<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警犬：</strong><br />\n可能調動警力，一更約5,000人，進入元朗做黃雀既可以係1,000-4,000人，會以tiderider為主力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據屯門及以7月21日既經驗，狗可能會完全不作為，或者偏向對家，因此會有可能搜查黑衫既身，令我方帶唔到裝入元朗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>裝備：</strong></span><br />\n據721經驗，普通打手會使用木棍、捧球棍、水喉通、藤條，刀手會拎開山刀，721中戴有白頭盔，並且不會設有防線，會由小巷街角突襲，並會無差別地攻撃途人，和理非亦有高風險受傷。<br />\n這些武器可能藏於屋與屋之間既隱蔽位、草叢、屋簷既地方，隨時準備好。當中水喉通會事先夾扁同整利，注意被捅，會有放血效果，有大機會致命。<br />\n<br />\n圍村人不乏做工程既人士，會有天拿水及汽油係村屋，而且有生日/新年放煙花既習慣，故推測圍頭佬懂得使用cocktail或其他類似易燃物品，但推測沒有防具。普通村民有可能使用任何家居物品高空擲物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警犬既防具有長盾、圓盾、速龍頭盔ops core highcut helmet、緑衫防暴有防火防裂衫。<br />\n攻擊方面，主要使用手臂既延伸警棍，長棍無咁傷，但伸縮棍有金屬頭擊中人會非常痛。警犬配有手槍，但甚少會使用。對於人群控制會用pepper spray、tear gas(手雷、槍發、子母彈，但子母彈據聞用晒)、有膠彈及布袋彈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzyLO4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzyLO4b.png&h=85fef32c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇準備應付上面所有既野千奇唔好入村！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa51f7227fa324428fd5185ccd6c29acbab6982","tid":1362011,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6528a28c894b5457d7de344b2713b39964a5d84c","tid":1362011,"uid":108331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"727 元朗見"},{"pid":"b8ab875bfbd2367ebfd2d250cc5cb020b8e21bec","tid":1362011,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:51:03.000Z","msg":"認真post 大力推<br />\n齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba19325aae82cab74b73b599bf5333ec1ebd53f","tid":1362011,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af2ebddfed940e50637c3f27a7a4da39f614840","tid":1362011,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:52:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb65f97b4837b887e43fbcb51b3f3b9f7981bf82","tid":1362011,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:53:27.000Z","msg":"元朗見<br />\n大家保護好自己 <br />\n對準政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca0057366a74d03d90afa55dec79fa23cbcb7b","tid":1362011,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:53:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"42543d6c0c76683c705a4d60392ecce54799da68","tid":1362011,"uid":259515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"另外大家可以摷返90年代 差佬攻入 上水嗰啲鄉村 full gear都打咗成日<br />\n評估一下入村可唔可行"},{"pid":"640b9ba7179f5232708d98d335e4d52284e7a4b0","tid":1362011,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:56:00.000Z","msg":"我地嘅敵人唔係村民 係政府黑警黑社會<br />\n留翻彈藥皇天擊殺佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42d04c2142737f0617b9f6a57bd6075563fe1e2","tid":1362011,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c42d2f3a630fa151f93f127770afe9c4b05bf4b","tid":1362011,"uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1f059bddac4c490c15fc8338cef23425af052776","tid":1362011,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:01:41.000Z","msg":"有用post要大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b621274614d491e7d6734c3283ed258394b7ab88","tid":1362011,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"要推俾全世界睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e8669bcb78136fc07ebcdf14de0d257f407177","tid":1362011,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n[置頂] 打完飛機未，打完就入黎傾正經野呀！！ 727 反黑遊行 5+1 訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpKaqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpKaqS</a>"},{"pid":"e0cc79464bbdf6f6ba0cc4ffa6d756457ff267b5","tid":1362011,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"push also"},{"pid":"b29fc1a5ee7eb1b6bdc91b25a3c786d85e0678db","tid":1362011,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:04:37.000Z","msg":"大推<br />\n<br />\n求投<br />\n【最新進展】元朗遊行官方時間無得提早<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360015</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a7967c9b68a26ecabf4fe6da2687c935232429fb","tid":1362011,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90f06f4e596a5e20d3f2fda937198b9bd505a5e6","tid":1362011,"uid":76331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:06:16.000Z","msg":"其實除左金屬鑊蓋之外<br />\n其他都應該擋唔倒開山刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83cc5010f7448eb71aa4ccd6b1a68ed8a43649a","tid":1362011,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:06:31.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f710846e5d098bd8796d0611f92ce1999d9f69","tid":1362011,"uid":260180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:07:13.000Z","msg":"728"},{"pid":"8724aa0b8e0de4d067906582a9bcbcb56dbb3bf4","tid":1362011,"uid":283516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:08:27.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"12fec3ca5c4a3df4ee3df51ec3c5c81fc9c8a907","tid":1362011,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90f06f4e596a5e20d3f2fda937198b9bd505a5e6","tid":1362011,"uid":76331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:06:16.000Z","msg":"其實除左金屬鑊蓋之外<br />\n其他都應該擋唔倒開山刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:09:51.000Z","msg":"木板咪頂一下，之後就爛<br />\n<br />\n其實就算薄金屬都係一兩下，要厚到鐵鑊咁先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ea6bced9da4a2b842d99cbde79ea0823e3f89e","tid":1362011,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90f06f4e596a5e20d3f2fda937198b9bd505a5e6","tid":1362011,"uid":76331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:06:16.000Z","msg":"其實除左金屬鑊蓋之外<br />\n其他都應該擋唔倒開山刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:12:20.000Z","msg":"最怕會無差別攻擊 唔係前線都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea24e2bc5218293273236d8818f10169605a8511","tid":1362011,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9b4339c4505261e30ad82f87a3c4bc3c16930b5","tid":1362011,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:47:57.000Z","msg":"開得戰，不外乎天時地利人和 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">天時：</span></strong><br />\n1. 這次遊行召集時間 1630-2400(好似話想提早到1500), 但係大家都知香港人出名遲到，隨時入黑先行到，而黑社會話明黑，夜晚先係佢哋主場，加上記者要影到你都要有燈光。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 早一星期已經講到話要搞村，D村民一早有準備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">地利：</span></strong><br />\n圍村村口前面係car park 非常空曠，進入時被村民一目了然。入圍村只有一條路，會裝有CCTV。一入圍村，戰友會係入侵方，有好多隱蔽既小路只有村民先知道，入面既村屋又係村民既地盤，村民可以在天台扔花盆，佢地有大量大型車輛，可以係入村後隨時封路，四面受敵，前線要提防所有村入面既人。<br />\n係南邊圍入面有四個一級歷史建築&mdash;晉源押、同益棧、大王廟同埋玄關二帝廟，絕對唔可以毀壞。除外村內會有民居、村校同埋教會。<br />\n十八鄉因歷史問題，來往非常密切，南邊圍、西邊圍、東頭圍、英龍圍、大圍村合稱五和同氣連枝，北面仲有林氏山貝村，所以一旦有事，戰友要向南面退，大馬路地方有限，東南角是Yoho既地盤。人潮唯有向水門頭天橋撤﹐而落橋位係泰祥街水車館街，人煙密集。<br />\n十八鄉和八鄉村民來往頗密，平時村裡的活動亦會邀請對方參與，逃走時避免去錦上路方向。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人和：</span></strong><br />\n<strong>自已友：</strong>按前幾次經驗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00VeHm0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00VeHm0.png&h=d3c5a211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>對家：</strong><br />\n據報，係7月21日，白衫有500-800人，當中包括睇水、車隊，相信打手有300人。而整個幫會好大機會有上千人，亦有未知多少刀手。<br />\n刀方面以開山刀為主。佢地重視威信建立，會因內部傷亡而報復。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而香港原居民有70萬人，是次既事件由南邊圍(及十八鄉部份其他鄉村)既鄉黑所為。<br />\n圍村人非常重視祠堂同圍村傳統，將祠堂視為社交重地及集體回憶，若然燒村/祠堂就會得罪本來不涉事既居民，包括中立甚至是黃營的村民。另外，佢地有不少祠堂，會有燒錯祠堂，樹立不必要敵人既可能。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n村民對外非常團結，村民之間社交網絡完整，會將村內發生既事以whatsapp通報全村。我地早一星期已經開始召集人手，放風燒村毀祠，咁樣就算搬出村外既村民都會返去元朗入面保護家園，巴打搵咗十八鄉既人口分佈，如下圖所示:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inpryuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinpryuM.png&h=7e498f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ni.e. 會出動的原居民(20-60 男丁) 有機會過5000<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警犬：</strong><br />\n可能調動警力，一更約5,000人，進入元朗做黃雀既可以係1,000-4,000人，會以tiderider為主力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據屯門及以7月21日既經驗，狗可能會完全不作為，或者偏向對家，因此會有可能搜查黑衫既身，令我方帶唔到裝入元朗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>裝備：</strong></span><br />\n據721經驗，普通打手會使用木棍、捧球棍、水喉通、藤條，刀手會拎開山刀，721中戴有白頭盔，並且不會設有防線，會由小巷街角突襲，並會無差別地攻撃途人，和理非亦有高風險受傷。<br />\n這些武器可能藏於屋與屋之間既隱蔽位、草叢、屋簷既地方，隨時準備好。當中水喉通會事先夾扁同整利，注意被捅，會有放血效果，有大機會致命。<br />\n<br />\n圍村人不乏做工程既人士，會有天拿水及汽油係村屋，而且有生日/新年放煙花既習慣，故推測圍頭佬懂得使用cocktail或其他類似易燃物品，但推測沒有防具。普通村民有可能使用任何家居物品高空擲物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警犬既防具有長盾、圓盾、速龍頭盔ops core highcut helmet、緑衫防暴有防火防裂衫。<br />\n攻擊方面，主要使用手臂既延伸警棍，長棍無咁傷，但伸縮棍有金屬頭擊中人會非常痛。警犬配有手槍，但甚少會使用。對於人群控制會用pepper spray、tear gas(手雷、槍發、子母彈，但子母彈據聞用晒)、有膠彈及布袋彈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzyLO4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzyLO4b.png&h=85fef32c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇準備應付上面所有既野千奇唔好入村！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oxNtm9AbaFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoxNtm9AbaFs&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=7c273b25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oxNtm9AbaFs</a>"},{"pid":"4c2b46aba0963b046b57abf7000e51c5cc2adb25","tid":1362011,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:19:50.000Z","msg":"元朗見"},{"pid":"e4087d9921275e64fdaceaf68ad9963cc65b878c","tid":1362011,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42543d6c0c76683c705a4d60392ecce54799da68","tid":1362011,"uid":259515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"另外大家可以摷返90年代 差佬攻入 上水嗰啲鄉村 full gear都打咗成日<br />\n評估一下入村可唔可行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"個陣因咩事要打入村"},{"pid":"cb251f6122cc2b2d4248c215c12830aab0ce9ba2","tid":1362011,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4087d9921275e64fdaceaf68ad9963cc65b878c","tid":1362011,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42543d6c0c76683c705a4d60392ecce54799da68","tid":1362011,"uid":259515,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"另外大家可以摷返90年代 差佬攻入 上水嗰啲鄉村 full gear都打咗成日<br />\n評估一下入村可唔可行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"個陣因咩事要打入村"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:20:32.000Z","msg":"收地"},{"pid":"99b444dfa05a8c15aedb44137b1cec45dde51b24","tid":1362011,"uid":34835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:22:10.000Z","msg":"光復元朗要解決民鬥民，唔駛畀條命老黑嘅方法，就係圍18鄉委會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ed69aec11d147db06756000bdbb6084717953e30","tid":1362011,"uid":287654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4020a84437e6c9aa08338c19f3a2781385a7ac64","tid":1362011,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:27:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/429266683934176/videos/1333613590121146/?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARB9K8T52dNzr81YE2LgVs5mI9Pbr-ND10pTQUWEzEXymNsMeeQQT0hDXsVt0ZPJ03ZHMgoDn6jhl9GNjPvwDw0Y-JCRo1xf3CcG8JuynRIFtjRmwypNscjOde4MpFjs-IlcK78fKTSpjIZBfvzV8YrV